Fuzzy people , floating people
During his <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">four - and - a - half years</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Paris</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Hsia</ENAMEX> lived in a tiny garret in the red light district with barely enough room to stand up in .
