Going home
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Hsia</ENAMEX> returned to <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">1992</ENAMEX> , after <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">three decades</ENAMEX> away .
